                    <h1 class="domdom">06</h1>

                    <h1>Film: <a href="/on/film/1065">I Will Walk Like A Crazy Horse (1973)</a></h1>

                    <h2>6 Mar 2013, 7:30 p.m.</h2>

                    <p>Cinematic surrealism and chaotic violence feature in this great film from the Spanish director of Viva La Muerte. Running away from the police, a man goes to the desert where he meets an uncivilized man with a special link with “Mother-Earth”.</p>

