                    <h1 class="domdom">15</h1>

                    <h1>Film: <a href="/on/film/1067">A Lizard In A Woman’S Skin (1971) + Euro-Disco In The Bar</a></h1>

                    <h2>15 Mar 2013, 7:30 p.m.</h2>

                    <p>Psychedelic nightmares, LSD use and mysterious murders feature in this Italian giallo set in London. A young woman is accused of murdering her hippy neighbour after dreaming it exactly as it happened…</p>

