                    <h1 class="domdom">17</h1>

                    <h1>Film: <a href="/on/film/1068">Vampyros Lesbos (1971)</a></h1>

                    <h2>17 Mar 2013, 7:30 p.m.</h2>

                    <p>With a great psychedelic score that became a hit in the British charts in the 1990s (in the album Sexadelic Dance Party), this is an erotic horror tale about a vixen vampiress seducing and killing women to appease her insatiable thirst for female blood. </p>

